items.badge_description: It's New Brew Thursday! Drink a new beer on three Thursdays in a 30 day period! Find out how New Brew Thursday was started, and catch up on old episodes.

Its been a long day and now its time for a reward. Crisp, tasty and refreshing, enjoy that delicious fruit beer! That's 10 different beers with the style of Fruit Beer or Sour - Fruited. Try 5 more for Level 3.

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly whats on tap! That's 5 check-ins at venue that is verified. Try 5 more for Level 2!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 70 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 15!

items.checkin_comment: Nice to find again, still good beer.

items.badge_description: Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 125 distinct venues!

items.checkin_comment: Don't get any coconut, or tiny - nice beer though.

user.bio: Mad keen homebrewer and all round beer geek.

items.checkin_comment: Don't recall a coconut flavour. Good beer but. Would revisit as a standalone.
